“Hey, hey shut the fuck up. I was just trying to help…”
I can't. I can't breathe.
“…. can't get in trouble again. Fuck. Fuck!” He curses. He sounds
scared too. That only makes me panic more. He cries out as my teeth dig
into the flesh of his hand, shoving me forward so hard my head snaps
