The world has a habit of seeming perfectly normal before
everything spirals entirely out of control. Eating a midday snack of yogurt
before finding your dad slumped in his chair after he sucked off a shotgun.
Moments like that, sitting there with that bowl of vanilla yogurt and the kiss
